  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\"><img alt=\"House Stark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/50px-House_Stark.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/75px-House_Stark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/100px-House_Stark.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> King</span><br />Dorren Stark</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\"><img alt=\"House Stark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/50px-House_Stark.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/75px-House_Stark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/100px-House_Stark.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Full name</th><td>\nDorren Stark</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/King_in_the_North\" title=\"King in the North\">King in the North</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">Northmen</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Dorren Stark</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/King_in_the_North\" title=\"King in the North\">King in the North</a> and head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a> before the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_Conquest\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"War of Conquest\">War of Conquest</a>. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dorren_Stark&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Doren is mentioned in an account of the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a>. During his rule the Night's Watch fought <a href=\"/index.php/Giants\" title=\"Giants\">giants</a> and traded with the <a href=\"/index.php/Children_of_the_forest\" title=\"Children of the forest\">children of the forest</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dorren_Stark&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_6\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 6\">Chapter 6</a>, Jon I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403221948\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.064 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.246 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 518/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10993/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6752/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 436/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 517/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.160/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.47 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  235.783      1 -total\n 97.59%  230.095      1 Template:Infobox_monarch\n 96.69%  227.970      1 Template:Infobox\n 12.37%   29.174     14 Template:Infobox_value\n  3.79%    8.932      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.78%    4.207      1 Template:Ref\n  1.19%    2.803      1 Template:Ref/core\n  0.56%    1.329      1 Template:References\n  0.39%    0.918      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:3